#

Avocado Pineapple Salsa

10 min
$5
120 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeVegan

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

EasyFreshAppetizer

Description

A refreshing, zesty blend of creamy avocado and sweet pineapple, perfect as a dip or topping!

Ingredients

  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • pineapple: 1 cup, diced
  • red onion: 1/4 cup, finely chopped
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
